 God did not want to take the Israelites out of Egypt.

586
00:27:33,800 --> 00:27:35,800
 After they left Egypt,

587
00:27:35,800 --> 00:27:39,800
 they still had a heart for Egypt.

588
00:27:39,800 --> 00:27:41,800
 They wanted to return to the Egyptian Empire

589
00:27:41,800 --> 00:27:44,800
 because there was a stable and prosperous place.

590
00:27:44,800 --> 00:27:53,800
 God wanted to take Egypt out of the Israelites

591
00:27:53,800 --> 00:27:57,800
 and take the Pharaoh out of Egypt

592
00:27:57,800 --> 00:28:03,800
 and take the Pharaoh out of Egypt

593
00:28:03,800 --> 00:28:05,800
 and take away the idols

594
00:28:05,800 --> 00:28:07,800
 like Moses,

595
00:28:07,800 --> 00:28:09,800
 who was a prosperous man

596
00:28:09,800 --> 00:28:11,800
 and a man of peace.

597
00:28:11,800 --> 00:28:15,800
 So that we can truly return to God

598
00:28:15,800 --> 00:28:18,800
 and be faithful to Him

599
00:28:18,800 --> 00:28:19,800
 and serve Him,

600
00:28:19,800 --> 00:28:23,800
 and be faithful to Him

601
00:28:23,800 --> 00:28:25,800
 Are we willing to do that?

602
00:28:25,800 --> 00:28:28,800
 Let God take away these idols

603
00:28:28,800 --> 00:28:31,800
 and let our hearts truly return to Him.

604
00:28:31,800 --> 00:28:36,800
 Let us pray with our hearts.

605
00:28:36,800 --> 00:28:38,800
 God, we know that Your way

606
00:28:38,800 --> 00:28:40,800
 and Your great command

607
00:28:40,800 --> 00:28:43,800
 is not what we humans think.

608
00:28:43,800 --> 00:28:44,800
 Your ultimate goal

609
00:28:44,800 --> 00:28:49,800
 is to make our lives belong to You.

610
00:28:49,800 --> 00:28:51,800
 God, we pray that You take away

611
00:28:51,800 --> 00:28:54,800
 the things we long for in our lives

612
00:28:54,800 --> 00:28:57,800
 like stability and prosperity

613
00:28:57,800 --> 00:29:01,800
 and the benefits that the land can give us.

614
00:29:01,800 --> 00:29:05,800
 God, let our lives truly belong to You.

615
00:29:05,800 --> 00:29:08,800
 Let You be our true Lord.

616
00:29:08,800 --> 00:29:10,800
 You continue to lead our lives

617
00:29:10,800 --> 00:29:13,800
 and the path ahead of us.

618
00:29:13,800 --> 00:29:17,800
 No matter what we are going through,

619
00:29:17,800 --> 00:29:20,800
 let us know that the ultimate goal

620
00:29:20,800 --> 00:29:24,800
 is not only to be free and carefree

621
00:29:24,800 --> 00:29:28,800
 but to be faithful to You.

622
00:29:28,800 --> 00:29:29,800
 Continue to train us,

623
00:29:29,800 --> 00:29:30,800
 continue to help us,

624
00:29:30,800 --> 00:29:31,800
 and nurture us

625
00:29:31,800 --> 00:29:32,800
 so that we can become

626
00:29:32,800 --> 00:29:37,800
 more fit for Your will.

